snippet.title: Stretch Armstrong: The Break Out | Official Trailer [HD] | Netflix After School
snippet.description:
Villains are rampaging through Charter City and the Flex Fighters — Jake, Ricardo and Nathan — need your help to halt the chaos. Help these heroes decide who to trust, when to fight and how to save the city.
